data.description:
$10,000 RATE BUY DOWN/ CLOSING COSTS INCENTIVE on full price offer!!! An ORIGINAL River Bend home with all of the charm - just updated! Welcome to your dream home nestled on a serene golf course in the heart of Floresville, Texas. This meticulously renovated gem boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, a versatile flex space, and 3 full baths, offering a harmonious blend of modern comfort and classic elegance. With 2,400 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, this home provides the perfect canvas for creating lasting memories.

Step inside and be captivated by the seamless fusion of contemporary design and timeless charm. The heart of the home is adorned with a spacious kitchen, complete with a double oven,  and ample storage. The open-concept layout effortlessly flows into the inviting living area, where natural light dances through the windows, illuminating the brand new flooring. You'll also find that there is a brand new roof, AC and water heater. 
Indulge in the luxury of a private primary suite, featuring a garden tub, walk in shower, and a walk-in closet. The additional three rooms offer comfort and versatility. Convenience meets luxury in this exceptional property, as it is not only a haven for golf enthusiasts but also conveniently located near renowned schools and just 30 minutes from San Antonio.  Don't miss your chance to own this piece of paradise in Floresville, Texas. Schedule your private tour today and experience this home for yourself.
